*Arun Kumar, Nitesh Saxena, Gene Tsudik, Ersin Uzun. â[[Caveat Emptor: A Comparative Study of Secure Device Pairing Methods|http://www.ersinuzun.com/pub/caveat.pdf]]â, in proceedings of the 7th Annual IEEE International Conference on Pervasive Computing and Communications (IEEE ~PerComâ09).
